column5: You can start by pressing "Apply for ID" and filling out the form.
You have to upload your documents. Atleast two document is Required. For more information you may ask me later.
You must upload a valid profile picture for your national I.D. To ensure validity follow this:
1. No Makeup#Newline2. Don't smile or frown#Newline3. No accessories#Newline4. No Eyewears#Newline5. No Contact lenses#Newline6. Proper Lighting
After your application is VALIDATED#Comma you may attend any registration center for your biometrics.
